	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example-&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;She was prepared to be magnanimous, prepared to feel compassion for him.&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
