&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Portable&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;quot;Portable&amp;quot; specifically refers to objects that are designed to be easily carried or moved.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word derives from the Latin word &amp;quot;portare,&amp;quot; which means &amp;quot;to carry.&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;(जिसे आसानी से हिलाया या कहीं ले जाया जा सके; सुवाह्य)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Commonly used to describe electronic devices such as laptops, speakers, and other items that are intentionally designed to be easily transportable.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Items labeled as portable are typically lightweight and compact, making them convenient for transport.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;A portable Bluetooth speaker is designed to be lightweight and easy to carry, making it convenient for outdoor activities.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Therefore, the correct example is &lt;strong&gt;option 4.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Option 1: Mobile: Typically refers to the ability to move freely or be easily moved, but it is not as specific as &amp;quot;portable&amp;quot; when describing ease of carrying.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Option 2: Potable: Refers to water that is safe to drink, unrelated to the ease of carrying.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Option 3: Briefcase: A specific object that can be carried easily but does not generalize the concept of ease of transportation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dotage&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
